Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.85,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.57,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:13.74,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:18.87,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:31.63,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:40.06,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:51.94,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.20,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.99,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:02.83,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:08.33,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:17.63,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:27.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're my first friend ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:33.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:34.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:37.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you ask Rem to kill L?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:39.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:41.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Light to love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:44.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and I will be grateful.\NThat would be my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:50.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll kill L for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L will die,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:54.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So when should I kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take me to wherever he is,\NI can kill him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:07.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be done\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:09.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still too soon to\Nmake a decision now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:17.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you an answer after\NI think of a way to kill him tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:24.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, no matter what,\Ndon't kill him until I give the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:25.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, concerning L...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:31.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll promise...only about L though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:35.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, give me\Nyour cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time!\NTell me yours, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't give you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?! We're lovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm under surveillance\Nby the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police these days can listen\Nin on specific phone conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one of\Nmy own cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:02.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up with three after\Nusing them for different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:03.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Using your phone would\Nprobably be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you\Na love call every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also send you\Na lot of text messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:12.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll keep it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the only one\Nmaking calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll only tell you what\Nyou need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:21.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to call?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:27.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call even if I'm not\Ngoing to execute L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't sound like something\Na lover would call about,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can talk about love afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well Misa,\Ngo home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why? It's only 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The time for lovers has\Njust begun, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go get dinner,\Nlook at the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and after that, the main event...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:47.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:03:59.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:03.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:07.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, when you're talking\Noutside with Rem,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,whisper and make sure that\Nno one's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Ryuk and I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:13.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the intrusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, come again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That kiss was so sudden,\Nit surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to keep\NMisa deeply in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:30.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:34.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, I need to decide\Nif I should kill L tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L hasn't made himself public yet.\NSo if Ryuga dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:42.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to prepare for people to be\Nmore suspicious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:43.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were hesitating
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because he said that\Nyou were his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:52.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend? I was just giving him\Nwhat he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:56.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning, I've said\Nthat if it's friendship he wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:03.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga is Light Yagami's superficial friend.\NBut L is Kira's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, L is my enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Ryuga's revealed\Nthat he's L, I must kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill L with an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:24.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there won't be many who would\Nsuspect that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if someone does suspect,\Nthere's no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:30.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only speculate what\Nwill be done after L dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all a wager now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:40.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will be L's-\Nno Ryuga/Ryuzaki's date of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:48.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Snack crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:56.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:04.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die within the next few days,\Nyour son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:07.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What are you\Ntalking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:17.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure that you\Nhave ready access to Watari,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:24.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said he was almost entirely cleared,\Nbut I want the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How likely is it that he's -?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know how I truly feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This has never happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira and the Second Kira\Nare working together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:44.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I might not be analyzing\Nthe situation calmly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:51.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be considering him a suspect\Njust because there's nobody else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:57.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm killed now,\Nplease assume that your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice\Nbut to make a sneak attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:04.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all a wager now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know how to swim with the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:45.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada, I want to talk to\Nhim for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we continue this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:55.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't you say that you were afraid\Nto appear in front of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:03.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that as long\Nas you're not Kira, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one on\Nthe outside who knows I'm L...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:10.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I've told everyone at headquarters\Nthat if I die in the next few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:15.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to assume that you're Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that\Nyou've been lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I've been taking\Nbreaks from school,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I came out for a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I don't die,\Ncollege is a fun place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When you're not here,\Nit's so boring
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because there's no one who can\Nmatch my level of conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that explains why\Nyou're with the "brilliant" Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:45.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really all right\Nto kill him today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:49.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...As soon as I decided\NI should kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he suddenly appears to\Ndistract me from my decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to prevent me from killing him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly what he wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we have some cake\Nin the cafeteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:05.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... My next lecture was canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:06.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they have shortcake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-! There you are-!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I came because I had\Na photo shoot nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-! You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so unique and cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...I've won-!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa can see Ryuga 's real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:35.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Light's girlfriend, Misa Amane.\NPleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hideki Ryuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he has the same first name\Nand last name as that idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:48.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...it's different from\Nthe name I'm seeing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:53.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga, coming out this time\Nhas backfired on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he laughing?\NDoes this mean he noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he's guessed that\Nshe's the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way he\Nwould be laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a huge fan of yours\Nsince the August issue of "Eighteen."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really? I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that girl.\NIsn't she Misa-Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. It's Misa-Misa-!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Misa-Misa?!\N- The real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have guessed\Nthat I'd be discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if there were\Na lot of young people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:31.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you.\NI'll do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on-?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who touched my butt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How disgraceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive anyone who\Nwould take advantage of this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga! You're so funny!.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:53.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to touch her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:58.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I want to ask Misa\Nwhat L's name is as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but these people are in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:01.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:03.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to\Nbe late again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, Yoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:08.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Misa's out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to give her a call\Nand ask her for L's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you after work, Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we go, Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, could you go on ahead?\NI need to go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:02.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I could discover\Nyour name and kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I could discover\Nyour name and kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Hello"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this cell phone must have\Nbeen dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by someone in\Nthat commotion earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard... He must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... That's Misa's cell phone, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:29.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga probably thinks he's won,\Nbut Misa has another phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I call that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this time...\Nit's my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:37.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I see. We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:51.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be good and\Nbad news to you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa Amane has just been\Ntaken into custody
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,under suspicion of being the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When in the world did\Nhe find out about Misa-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought he'd catch her\Nthis quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:07.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were hairs and fibers,\Namong other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,attached to the masking tape\Nsealing the tapes the Second Kira sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We discovered many matching samples\Nof evidence in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:19.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There will probably be a riot if\Nwe charge her with being the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're telling the public that\Nshe's voluntarily coming with us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because her manager is\Nsuspected of drug possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth will probably\Nnever go public...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:35.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That video. I should have\Ndestroyed all the evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Ryuga chose to\Nprotect himself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by being with me instead of hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He confronted the\Nheart of the matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This wager... is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:53.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The challenge is just beginning, L...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, has she said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she hasn't said anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a visual of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:17.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've apprehended her\Nas the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This, at the very least,\Nis necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, there was enough evidence\Nin Amane's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:41.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to mark her as\Nthe Second Kira, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:47.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all we have to do is\Nmake her tell us how she kills...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:52.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether she knows Kira,\Nand if she knows who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari. Take the proper precautions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but do whatever needs to be done,\NI don't care what,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to get her to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:00.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Mr. Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably going to bring\Nin Light to testify,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as the prime suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, Amane's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me visuals...and sound quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:40.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally after three days, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:47.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me... Hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was too much\Nfor a young girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be at her limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa Amane, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:07.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you...\NPlease kill me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:11.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because you admit\Nto being the Second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No-! I don't know anything\Nabout the Second Kira-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:19.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore...!\NI'd rather die...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry! Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to\Nkill me immediately, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa...do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to kill you-?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore... Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill you, I'll kill Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all his...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:52.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No...\NKill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:56.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... You want so badly...\Nto die for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! If you won't kill me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good, Watari...\NDon't let her bite her tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:13.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that these are\Njust actions
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,controlled by Kira before death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I offered to help Misa escape,\Nbut she refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:31.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably thought it would\Nget you in trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:34.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since the police think that\Nshe has special powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:38.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And when she was\Nat her wit's end,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she started to ask me to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because she\Nwants you to love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:51.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much she asked,\NI couldn't kill her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:53.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear watching her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:57.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was only one way\Nto save her from that suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:01.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forfeiting ownership\Nof the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:02.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she forfeits ownership\Nof the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,all memories related to\Nthe Death Note will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All memories of murders\Nshe committed with her notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:16.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the fact that you are Kira,\Nwill disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa will not reveal your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:25.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Misa will no longer\Nbe able to see Ryuk or me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.60,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(458,459)}Several hours earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:28.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,395)}Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:33.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You will forget\Neverything about Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:41.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. The human you\Nlove is Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those emotions will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Misa, forfeit ownership\Nof the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and leave everything to Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:30.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa no longer owns the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well, Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was beginning to think\Nthat was the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:38.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If her memories of\Nthe Death Note are erased,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's not impossible\Nto release Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:45.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami, I proposed this\Nto Misa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:51.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I knew this is the method\Nyou would have desired the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:56.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't save Misa, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have a good idea\Nof what L is going to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good bye, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:18.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:28.68,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:34.06,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:43.07,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:49.45,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:54.04,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:59.75,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:07.17,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:12.39,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:23.11,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:28.95,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:41.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I know I probably look\Npretty bad in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:44.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but this useless pride... I'll just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:46.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,get rid of it!
